			<div class="locations">London, Barcelona, New York</div>
			<div class="contact">
				<a href="mailto:paul.ashot@icloud.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">paul.ashot@icloud.com</a> ·
				(646) 996 5037 ·
				<a href="https://pauldiazashot.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">pauldiazashot.com</a> ·
				@supersonicsines
			</div>
			<div class="work-auth">Right to work: UK, US, EU</div>
		</header>

		<div class="cv-body">
			<Collapsible title="Introduction">
				<p>
					I'm a founder-operator. The short version of my work is two seasons: four
					years on the founding team of <HoverCard term="GMX">
						<span class="hc-p">A decentralised perpetual exchange. Three-person founding team, no outside investment, $450M+ TVL and $40M+ in annualised fee revenue at peak.</span>
						<span class="hc-p"><em>[PLACEHOLDER — replace with 200–300 word essay covering: GLP unified-liquidity-pool design, your specific role in growth/partnerships, the Arbitrum migration, the deal arithmetic that made it work.]</em></span>
						<span class="hc-p further-reading">→ <a href="https://gmx.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">gmx.io</a> · <a href="https://defillama.com/protocol/gmx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DeFiLlama TVL chart</a></span>
					</HoverCard>, then three years of independent AI deployments. Native English, fluent Russian, fluent Spanish; right to work in the UK, US, and EU.
				</p>
				<p>
					Each role below opens as a window — click to read more. The PDF version is
					<a href="/Paul_Diaz_Ashot_CV.pdf" download target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>.
				</p>
			</Collapsible>

			<Collapsible title="Experience">
				<div class="role">
					<button class="role-trigger" data-window-trigger="portico" aria-haspopup="dialog">
						<b>Portico Ventures</b> — <em>Managing Partner</em>
					</button>
